New York (CNN Business)The Omicron variant is driving a surge in Covid-19 cases across the country, sickening Americans and upending our daily routines. We want to hear how Omicron is affecting your life. Are you sick and unable to work? Healthy and picking up extra shifts? Seeing disruptions to your daily routine because of schedule changes at schools, your bus route, grocery store, or elsewhere? Share your story with us.  